OL,6,FPeople in the Borders will be asked to
OL,7,Fhave their say on the future of
OL,8,Fleisure, cultural and sporting
OL,9,Ffacilities in the region, as Clare
OL,10,FMcNeil reports.
OL,12,FA public consultation on the future of
OL,13,Fleisure, cultural and sporting
OL,14,Ffacilities in the Borders will be
OL,15,Flaunched next month.
