OL,3,CConsultation on future of facilities
OL,4,Cas job losses and closures proposed
OL,6,FScottish Borders Council met today to
OL,7,Fdiscuss the findings of a report
OL,8,Frecommending the closure of a string
OL,9,Fof museums, libraries, and community
OL,10,Fcentres run on its behalf by the
OL,11,Fcharitable trust Live Borders.
OL,13,FSince the pandemic, the organisation
OL,14,Fhas struggled financially. Last year,
OL,15,Fthe local authority took back control
OL,16,Fof some of its services before
OL,17,Fcommissioning a review of its
OL,18,Foperations.
