OL,3,CConsultation on future of facilities
OL,4,Cas job losses and closures proposed
OL,6,FThe report, by independent consultants
OL,7,FIntegratis, said Live Borders faces
OL,8,F"an unsustainable deficit, requiring
OL,9,Furgent action to reduce costs and
OL,10,Fincrease revenues."
OL,12,FIt's made up of more than 150 pages,
OL,13,Fincluding recommendations for staffing
OL,14,Fcuts and venue closures, which it's
OL,15,Fprojected will save around #2.5-#3m.
OL,17,FIt's proposed that around 30 venues
OL,18,Facross the region be closed and 50
OL,19,Ffull-time posts cut.
OL,26,@pD@AOUrD@SO]
