OL,3,CConsultation on future of facilities
OL,4,Cas job losses and closures proposed
OL,6,FBut both Live Borders and Scottish
OL,7,FBorders Council have said it's
OL,8,Fimportant that the public have their
OL,9,Fsay before any decisions are made.
OL,11,FAmong the facilities recommended for
OL,12,Fclosure are Tweedbank Community
OL,13,FCentre, Langlee Community Centre, and
OL,14,FNewtown St Boswells Community Wing.
OL,16,FIt's advised that libraries in
OL,17,FEyemouth, Earlston, Coldstream and
OL,18,FHawick are closed or consolidated with
OL,19,Fother services.
