OL,3,CConsultation on future of facilities
OL,4,Cas job losses and closures proposed
OL,6,FSelkirk Swimming Pool and the Queen's
OL,7,FLeisure Centre are proposed to close,
OL,8,Fwith Tweedbank Bowling Centre turned
OL,9,Finto a fitness gym as Tri Fitness is
OL,10,Frelocated there.
OL,12,FThe report also advised that
OL,13,FJedburgh's Laidlaw Pool should remain
OL,14,Fclosed.
OL,16,FHistoric venues such as Sir Walter
OL,17,FScott's courtroom in Selkirk and Old
OL,18,FGala House are also proposed for
OL,19,Fclosure.
