OL,3,CConsultation on future of facilities
OL,4,Cas job losses and closures proposed
OL,6,FChair of Live Borders Bill Douglas has
OL,7,Fsaid: "We just can't keep going at
OL,8,Fthis rate, there's an unsustainable
OL,9,Fposition in terms of the cost to run
OL,10,Fall the facilities we have out there
OL,11,Fat the moment.
OL,13,F"I understand the public's concern at
OL,14,Fthe moment, but it's important to
OL,15,Fstress that no decisions have been
OL,16,Fmade yet.
OL,26,@oD@GOUuD@AOU
