OL,3,CConsultation on future of facilities
OL,4,Cas job losses and closures proposed
OL,6,F"I see that as Live Borders'
OL,7,Fopportunity now to engage with the
OL,8,Fcommunities, talk about the services
OL,9,Fthey want delivered from if it's not
OL,10,Fthose premises and other premises, but
OL,11,Ffrom somewhere, and then grow them
OL,12,Ffrom there. But it's all about the
OL,13,Fcommunity to me. And how do we work to
OL,14,Fdeliver those things."
