OL,3,CConsultation on future of facilities
OL,4,Cas job losses and closures proposed
OL,6,FCouncil Leader Euan Jardine said:
OL,7,F"This is a national issue, it's not
OL,8,Fjust a Scottish Borders issue. We're
OL,9,Ftackling it head-on. What really came
OL,10,Fout of the meeting today was the
OL,11,Fpassion of the councillors about how
OL,12,Fmuch this means to communities.
OL,14,F"And nobody knows our communities
OL,15,Fbetter than those who live there ,and
OL,16,Fthat is why we're coming out with a
OL,17,Fconsultation now before making any
OL,18,Fdecisions.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
